text:
Yes, good work!
How was the lesson, Chiyuki?

I might be feeling a little overwhelmed by the
energetic vibe of everyone in Houkura!

And Natsuha-chan,
did you do some extra practice this morning?
I happened to see you, and I was surprised!

Oh, you saw that...?
You should have said something...

I didn't want to disturb you,
you seemed so focused, Natsuha-chan.

I was just tired from the lessons...
You're amazing.

No, it's just that this level
of exercise suits my body.

So there's nothing particularly
amazing about it.
Everyone has their own way of doing things, Chiyuki.

My own way of doing things, huh...
Hehe, it feels like you've cheered me up a bit.
